Pendulum Effect
 When a Pendulum Monster you control is destroyed by battle: You can Special Summon this card from your Pendulum Zone.

 Monster Effect
 Once per turn, if a Pendulum Monster you control destroys an opponent's monster by battle, after damage calculation: You can have that monster you control gain 200 ATK until the end of the Battle Phase, also that monster can make a second attack in a row.
